title: Mark my words. Popplio's going to be a badass.

embed.description: Let's shoot for 1,000 likes? Hype is so real with this most recent leak! We get a glimpse of what the final evolutions of the new Pokemon Sun and Moon starters might look like! These new typings are very unique and haven't been used a ton.

body: Potentially Water/Fighting? Popplio's gonna be slapping some bitches, m8.
